r="ltr">is easy</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَقِيمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and establish</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّلَوٲةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the prayer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَءَاتُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and give</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلزَّكَوٲةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the zakah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَقْرِضُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and loan</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَرْضًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a loan</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسَنًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">goodly.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُقَدِّمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you send forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَنفُسِكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for yourselves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَيْرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجِدُوهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will find it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">It</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَيْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) better</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَعْظَمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and greater</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَجْرًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) reward.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱسْتَغْفِرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And seek forgiveness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><